<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.2">
<l>kārmaṉṉu nīḷvicum pumkaṭa lumcuṭa rumnila ṉummalai yuntaṉṉuntit</l>
<l>tārmaṉṉu tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉi ṭantaṭa māmatiḷ cūḻntaḻa kāyakacci</l>
<l>tērmaṉṉu teṉṉava ṉaimuṉai yilceru viltiṟal vāṭṭiya tiṇcilaiyōṉ</l>
<l>pārmaṉṉu pallavar kōṉpaṇin tapara</l>
<l>mēccura viṇṇaka ramatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In fair Kacci encircled by great, wide walls, the place of the one</l>
<l rend="indent">with lotus[-like] eyes</l>
<l>In whose navel a blossom endures with the towering monsoon-filled skies,</l>
<l rend="indent">the sea, the sun, earth, and the mountains,</l>
<l>Is Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram where bowed the Pallava king</l>
<l rend="indent">who endures [long] on earth,</l>
<l>The one of the strong bow who destroyed on the battlefield</l>
<l rend="indent">the power of the southerner whose chariots abounded in combat.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
